{"tid":2423293,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"教育界「雙雄」子女外國路｜楊潤雄子女澳洲吸自由空氣 葉劉淑儀千金英國搵好工","createTime":"2021-02-26T00:00:30.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-26T09:39:24.000Z","uid":130626,"like":30,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"1d5d7f814cb5b91dcee2c6d9d3affe54dc11027a","tid":2423293,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T00:00:30.000Z","msg":"反送中風波後，政府將「民意對抗」歸究於香港教育制度，建制派動員高調批評通識教育累事，愛國教育不足，又指有教師「嚴重專業失德」而連續釘牌，教育界腥風血雨。立法會議員兼曾任教育事務委員會主席葉劉淑儀，亦欲強力加插幼稚園、中小學教科書及教材編製議程，企圖規管教科書內容限制學生，改革通識科。<br />\n<br />\n國民教育恐怕遲早捲土重來。教育局局長楊潤雄早前放風，要加速融合中港，建議在大灣區設立香港人就讀的中小學一條龍學校，並在境外考文憑試。<br />\n<br />\n兩大負責培育香港下一代的香港教育搞手，一早已將仔女送出香港，楊潤雄的子女更是外國出生。他們的下一代，在外國落地生根，接受的外國教育，在外國工作，充滿了自由的空氣。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.nextmgz.com/article/2_777249_0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.nextmgz.com%2Farticle%2F2_777249_0&d=6DLEtCU0DjtZYWozPjwd66nyrFheAedOz%2Bkyyi3ikZI%3D&h=d3c0a287\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.nextmgz.com%2Farticle%2F2_777249_0&h=21c262c6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.nextmgz.com/article/2_777249_0</a>"},{"pid":"ea431e64767859b93778ff3ed38480752361f7cd","tid":2423293,"uid":325200,"like":0,"dislike":13,"score":-13,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T00:06:00.000Z","msg":"佢個女...想屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"687f69a2fe3ef713cd433d683299f61da9f02dc7","tid":2423293,"uid":123289,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"ea431e64767859b93778ff3ed38480752361f7cd","tid":2423293,"uid":325200,"like":0,"dislike":13,"score":-13,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T00:06:00.000Z","msg":"佢個女...想屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T00:07:59.000Z","msg":"班左支美極返嚟未？"},{"pid":"9939ff8ace5be07d5c21894bfa6252bf35cdf291","tid":2423293,"uid":142097,"like":1,"disli